headline: Goldman CEO on Trump's call for semiannual earnings reports: 'I didn't know it was something I needed to think about'
summary: Goldman Sachs CEO David Solomon said he hasn't landed on a firm view about whether US public companies, including his own, should shift to reporting earnings half as often as the current standard.

headline: 3 Big Reasons GS Should Be On Your Watchlist
summary: Goldman Sachs currently trades at $793.50 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 307% since September 2020, tripling the S&P 500’s 101% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 35.4% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
